{"context":"ProductsService","level":"debug","message":"[DEBUG] Product: {\"id\":\"7851a4aa-90a5-4890-bb30-fbd05ec0455c\",\"sku\":\"WW-MRBJ-001-25-NF\",\"erpnextItemCode\":null,\"amazonAsin\":null,\"amazonFnsku\":null,\"amazonProductType\":null,\"upc\":null,\"flipkartSku\":null,\"thumbnailUrl\":null,\"name\":\"Woodwolf® Premium Wooden Storage Rack with Natural Jute Fabric Back Panel – Decorative Floating Cubby Organizer for Living Room & Kitchen (25, Natural Matte Finish)\",\"description\":\"Transform your kitchen or living space with this charming wooden wall-mounted mug display shelf, featuring a classic 3x3 grid layout with 9 individual compartments. Crafted from Pine wood with a Natural Matte Finish, with Backpanel material MDF + Lemination, this shelf beautifully combines functionality with premium elegance. The burlap-textured backing in each compartment adds a delightful contrast, making your favourite mugs and collectibles stand out as a curated display. Each cubby is generously sized to accommodate standard mugs with handles, keeping your collection organised and easily accessible. The shelf can be mounted on the wall to save counter space or placed on a flat surface, thanks to the included protective silicone bumper caps that prevent scratching. Whether you are a mug collector, a coffee enthusiast, or simply looking for a stylish storage solution, this display shelf is a perfect addition to any home. It also works wonderfully for displaying small figurines, succulents, or other decorative items.\",\"category\":\"BASE_PRODUCT\",\"brand\":\"Woodwolf\",\"uom\":\"Nos\",\"hsnCode\":null,\"gstRate\":\"18.00\",\"mrp\":\"0.00\",\"sellingPrice\":\"0.00\",\"costPrice\":\"0.00\",\"weight\":null,\"weightUom\":\"Kg\",\"images\":null,\"attributes\":{\"asin\":\"B0H7XK1GDL\",\"images\":[{\"images\":[{\"link\":\"https://m.media-amazon.com/images/I/611oV7KnXKL.jpg\",\"width\":1024,\"height\":1024,\"variant\":\"MAIN\"},{\"link\":\"https://m.media-amazon.com/images/I/41oYLd-5