{"context":"ProductsService","level":"debug","message":"[DYNAMIC-MAP] Mapping \"product_description\" = \"Transform any wall into a stunning display with the Woodwolf Wooden Wall Display Shelf. Featuring a 5x5 grid layout with 25 individual compartments, this rustic Walnut wood shelf is perfectly designed to showcase your favourite mugs, collectibles, or decorative items. Measuring 63.5 cm wide, 63.5 cm tall, and 9 cm deep, it offers ample space in each cubby whilst maintaining a compact, elegant profile in your living room or kitchen. Crafted from solid wood with a warm Walnut finish, the shelf weighs 2000 grams and can support up to 15 kg in total. It arrives pre-assembled, requiring only wall mounting using the included hardware — simply mark your wall, drill, insert wall plugs, and secure with screws. Each shelf panel is 15 mm thick, ensuring sturdy and reliable support. Care is simple — just wipe clean with a dry or slightly damp cloth. A beautiful and functional addition to any home interior.\" → \"description\" (Text Editor)","timestamp":"2026-07-18T11:52:43.872Z"}
