l compartments, perfect for organising and showcasing mugs, collectibles, and small decorative items.\",\"language_tag\":\"en_IN\",\"marketplace_id\":\"A21TJRUUN4KGV\"},{\"value\":\"STURDY NATURAL WOOD CONSTRUCTION: Crafted from solid wood with a rustic natural wood finish, measuring 41.25 cm wide x 41.25 cm tall x 9 cm deep with a shelf thickness of 15 mm.\",\"language_tag\":\"en_IN\",\"marketplace_id\":\"A21TJRUUN4KGV\"},{\"value\":\"WALL-MOUNTED DESIGN: Arrives pre-assembled and mounts securely to the wall using provided hardware; simply mark, drill, and fix in place for a clean, space-saving display.\",\"language_tag\":\"en_IN\",\"marketplace_id\":\"A21TJRUUN4KGV\"},{\"value\":\"GENEROUS WEIGHT CAPACITY: Supports up to 7 kg in total, making it suitable for holding mugs, small plants, books, and other lightweight decorative pieces with ease.\",\"language_tag\":\"en_IN\",\"marketplace_id\":\"A21TJRUUN4KGV\"},{\"value\":\"EASY MAINTENANCE: Requires minimal upkeep — simply wipe clean with a dry or slightly damp cloth to keep the shelf looking fresh and well-maintained.\",\"language_tag\":\"en_IN\",\"marketplace_id\":\"A21TJRUUN4KGV\"}],\"customPackerContactInformation\":[{\"value\":\"319, Sagar Complex, Joshonath Chowk, Bhavnagar, Gujarat - 364001\",\"language_tag\":\"en_IN\",\"marketplace_id\":\"A21TJRUUN4KGV\"}],\"customSpecificUsesForProduct\":[{\"value\":\"Mug Display\",\"language_tag\":\"en_IN\",\"marketplace_id\":\"A21TJRUUN4KGV\"},{\"value\":\"Cosmetics\",\"language_tag\":\"en_IN\",\"marketplace_id\":\"A21TJRUUN4KGV\"},{\"value\":\"Decorative Items\",\"language_tag\":\"en_IN\",\"marketplace_id\":\"A21TJRUUN4KGV\"}],\"customRecommendedUsesForProduct\":[{\"value\":\"Mug Display\",\"language_tag\":\"en_IN\",\"marketplace_id\":\"A21TJRUUN4KGV\"},{\"value\":\"Home Decor\",\"language_tag\":\"en_IN\",\"marketplace_id\":\"A21TJRUUN4KGV\"},{\"value\":\"Storage\",\"language_tag\":\"en_IN\",\"marketplace_id\":\"A21TJRUUN4KGV\"}],\"customRoomType\":[{\"value\":\"Living R