 secure with screws. Each shelf panel is 15 mm thick, ensuring sturdy and reliable support. Care is simple — just wipe clean with a dry or slightly damp cloth. A beautiful and functional addition to any home interior.\",\"language_tag\":\"en_IN\",\"marketplace_id\":\"A21TJRUUN4KGV\"}],\"shelf_bracket_shape\":[{\"value\":\"Square Grid\",\"language_tag\":\"en_IN\",\"marketplace_id\":\"A21TJRUUN4KGV\"}],\"is_assembly_required\":[{\"value\":true,\"marketplace_id\":\"A21TJRUUN4KGV\"}],\"assembly_instructions\":[{\"value\":\"Mount The Shelf On The Wall Using The Provided Hardware. Mark The Desired Position On The Wall, Drill Holes At The Marked Points, Insert Wall Plugs, And Secure The Shelf Using Screws. Ensure The Shelf Is Level Before Tightening Fully.\",\"language_tag\":\"en_IN\",\"marketplace_id\":\"A21TJRUUN4KGV\"}],\"item_depth_width_height\":[{\"depth\":{\"unit\":\"centimeters\",\"value\":9},\"width\":{\"unit\":\"centimeters\",\"value\":44},\"height\":{\"unit\":\"centimeters\",\"value\":44},\"marketplace_id\":\"A21TJRUUN4KGV\"}],\"item_package_dimensions\":[{\"width\":{\"unit\":\"centimeters\",\"value\":46},\"height\":{\"unit\":\"centimeters\",\"value\":46},\"length\":{\"unit\":\"centimeters\",\"value\":10},\"marketplace_id\":\"A21TJRUUN4KGV\"}],\"product_site_launch_date\":[{\"value\":\"2026-06-17T05:33:22.101Z\",\"marketplace_id\":\"A21TJRUUN4KGV\"}],\"recommended_browse_nodes\":[{\"value\":\"1380538031\",\"marketplace_id\":\"A21TJRUUN4KGV\"}],\"specific_uses_for_product\":[{\"value\":\"Mug Display\",\"language_tag\":\"en_IN\",\"marketplace_id\":\"A21TJRUUN4KGV\"},{\"value\":\"Books\",\"language_tag\":\"en_IN\",\"marketplace_id\":\"A21TJRUUN4KGV\"},{\"value\":\"Decorative Items\",\"language_tag\":\"en_IN\",\"marketplace_id\":\"A21TJRUUN4KGV\"}],\"packer_contact_information\":[{\"value\":\"319, Sagar Complex, Joshonath Chowk, Bhavnagar, Gujarat - 364001\",\"language_tag\":\"en_IN\",\"marketplace_id\":\"A21TJRUUN4KGV\"}],\"recommended_uses_for_product\":[{\"value\