{"context":"ProductsService","level":"debug","message":"[DYNAMIC-MAP] Mapping \"product_description\" = \"Transform any wall into a stunning display with the Woodwolf Wooden Wall Display Shelf. Featuring a 3x3 grid layout with 9 individual compartments, this rustic Walnut wood shelf is perfectly designed to showcase your favourite mugs, collectibles, or decorative items. Measuring 41.25 cm wide, 41.25 cm tall, and 9 cm deep, it offers ample space in each cubby whilst maintaining a compact, elegant profile in your living room or kitchen. Crafted from solid wood with a warm Walnut finish, the shelf weighs 700 grams and can support up to 7 kg in total. It arrives pre-assembled, requiring only wall mounting using the included hardware — simply mark your wall, drill, insert wall plugs, and secure with screws. Each shelf panel is 15 mm thick, ensuring sturdy and reliable support. Care is simple — just wipe clean with a dry or slightly damp cloth. A beautiful and functional addition to any home interior.\" → \"description\" (Text Editor)","timestamp":"2026-07-18T11:53:41.922Z"}
