{"context":"ProductsService","level":"debug","message":"[DYNAMIC-MAP] Mapping \"product_description\" = \"Transform any wall into a charming display with the Woodwolf Wooden Wall Display Shelf, featuring a 5x5 grid layout with 25 individual compartments. Crafted from solid wood with a beautiful walnut wood finish, Backpanel material MDF + Lemination, this rustic shelf is perfect for showcasing your favourite mug collection, small plants, trinkets, or decorative items. Measuring 63.5 cm wide x 63.5 cm tall x 9 cm deep, it offers ample space in each compartment while maintaining a compact, stylish profile. The shelf arrives pre-assembled, requiring only simple wall mounting using the provided hardware — compatible with wall studs or appropriate wall anchors. With a weight capacity of up to 18 kg, it is sturdy enough to hold a variety of items securely. Ideal for living rooms, kitchens, or home offices, this wall-mounted display shelf adds a warm, rustic charm to any interior. Care is simple — just wipe clean with a dry or slightly damp cloth to maintain its natural beauty.\" → \"description\" (Text Editor)","timestamp":"2026-07-18T11:54:08.610Z"}
