{"context":"ProductsService","level":"error","message":"Failed to push B0H662CNW7 to ERPNext. Payload: {\"item_code\":\"B0H662CNW7\",\"sku\":\"B0H662CNW7\",\"item_name\":\"Woodwolf® Wooden Display Shelf for Collectibles with Back Panel | Wall Mounted Shadow Box Shelf | 5x4 Grid Display Case | Miniature, Ceramic & Curio Organizer (Natural Clear Matte Finish)\",\"description\":\"Transform any bare wall into a stunning display with this beautifully crafted wall-mounted wooden shelf unit. Featuring a warm natural oak finish, this elegant piece showcases a grid-style layout with multiple individual compartments, perfectly sized to display cups, bowls, ceramics, and other cherished collectibles. The thoughtfully designed wooden pegs between each section add a distinctive architectural charm while keeping your displayed items neatly separated. With five rows and four columns of open cubbies, this shelf offers ample space to curate and showcase your favourite pottery, glassware, or decorative objects in an organised and visually appealing manner. The rich wood grain backdrop adds warmth and depth, making each displayed item stand out beautifully. Whether placed in a living room, kitchen, or study, this wall shelf brings a touch of Scandinavian-inspired minimalism to your home décor. Easy to mount and built to last, it is an ideal choice for collectors and design enthusiasts alike who wish to display their treasured pieces with style and sophistication.\",\"item_group\":\"Products\",\"custom_amazon\":1,\"disabled\":0,\"is_sales_item\":0,\"variant_of\":\"B0H662MQYQ\",\"attributes\":[{\"attribute\":\"Furniture_finish\",\"attribute_value\":\"Natural Clear Matte Finish\"}],\"image\":\"https://m.media-amazon.com/images/I/51zXhxEYrYL.jpg\",\"custom_thumbnail_image\":\"https://m.media-amazon.com/images/I/51zXhxEYrYL.jpg\",\"custom_amazon_product_type\":\"SHELF\",\"custom_number_of_packs\":1,\"custom_color\":\"Natural clear matte finish\",\"custom_number_of_pieces\":1,\"custom_numbe