{"context":"ProductsService","level":"debug","message":"[DYNAMIC-MAP] Mapping \"product_description\" = \"Transform any bare wall into a stunning focal point with this beautifully crafted solid wood wall-mounted display shelf. Featuring a distinctive geometric grid design, this shelf offers multiple open compartments arranged in an eye-catching cross-like pattern, making it as much a piece of wall art as it is a functional storage solution. Crafted from Pine wood with a warm, light oak finish, it blends seamlessly with modern, Scandinavian, and minimalist interiors alike. Each compartment is perfectly sized to display mugs, small plants, books, collectibles, and decorative accents. Whether mounted above a coffee station in the kitchen or used as a feature shelf in the living room or study, this versatile piece adds warmth and character to any space. The clean lines and natural wood grain give it a timeless appeal that complements a wide range of décor styles. Easy to mount on the wall, it keeps your favourite items organised and beautifully displayed. Please refer to the product dimensions before purchasing to ensure a proper fit for your space.\" → \"description\" (Text Editor)","timestamp":"2026-07-18T11:54:42.433Z"}
