{"context":"ProductsService","level":"debug","message":"[DYNAMIC-MAP] Mapping \"product_description\" = \"Transform any bare wall into a stylish and functional display with this minimalist wooden wall shelf. Crafted from solid natural wood with a warm, honey-toned finish, this vertical wall-mounted shelf features three open tiers that are perfectly spaced to hold your everyday essentials. Measuring 90 cm in height and 10 cm in width and depth, its slim, space-saving design makes it ideal for bedrooms, or living areas where floor space is limited. Each tier provides a sturdy ledge to neatly organise small plants, decorative vases, books, or knick-knacks. The natural wood grain texture adds a touch of warmth and Scandinavian-inspired charm to any interior décor. Whether you use it to display your favourite skincare products or a small floral arrangement, this elegant shelf brings both order and beauty to your space. Easy to mount on the wall, it is a versatile addition to any home.\" → \"description\" (Text Editor)","timestamp":"2026-07-18T11:54:48.345Z"}
