IN\",\"marketplace_id\":\"A21TJRUUN4KGV\"}],\"customAmazonBulletPoint\":[{\"value\":\"9-COMPARTMENT DESIGN: Features a 3x3 grid layout with individual cubbies, perfect for organising and displaying up to 9 mugs or collectibles.\",\"language_tag\":\"en_IN\",\"marketplace_id\":\"A21TJRUUN4KGV\"},{\"value\":\"WALL-MOUNTED OR FREESTANDING: Versatile shelf can be hung on the wall or placed on a countertop, making it ideal for kitchens, living rooms, or home offices.\",\"language_tag\":\"en_IN\",\"marketplace_id\":\"A21TJRUUN4KGV\"},{\"value\":\"PINE WOOD CONSTRUCTION: Crafted from Pine wood with a natural matte finish, Backpanel material MDF + Lemination, adding a rustic yet modern aesthetic to any home décor.\",\"language_tag\":\"en_IN\",\"marketplace_id\":\"A21TJRUUN4KGV\"},{\"value\":\"JUTE FABRIC BACKING: Each compartment features a textured jute fabric back panel that enhances the visual appeal and beautifully showcases displayed items.\",\"language_tag\":\"en_IN\",\"marketplace_id\":\"A21TJRUUN4KGV\"}],\"customPackerContactInformation\":[{\"value\":\"319, Sagar Complex, Joshonath Chowk, Bhavnagar, Gujarat - 364001\",\"language_tag\":\"en_IN\",\"marketplace_id\":\"A21TJRUUN4KGV\"}],\"customSpecificUsesForProduct\":[{\"value\":\"Mug Display\",\"language_tag\":\"en_IN\",\"marketplace_id\":\"A21TJRUUN4KGV\"}],\"customRecommendedUsesForProduct\":[{\"value\":\"Mug Display\",\"language_tag\":\"en_IN\",\"marketplace_id\":\"A21TJRUUN4KGV\"},{\"value\":\"Desk\",\"language_tag\":\"en_IN\",\"marketplace_id\":\"A21TJRUUN4KGV\"},{\"value\":\"Balcony\",\"language_tag\":\"en_IN\",\"marketplace_id\":\"A21TJRUUN4KGV\"},{\"value\":\"Home Decor\",\"language_tag\":\"en_IN\",\"marketplace_id\":\"A21TJRUUN4KGV\"},{\"value\":\"Kitchen\",\"language_tag\":\"en_IN\",\"marketplace_id\":\"A21TJRUUN4KGV\"},{\"value\":\"Storage\",\"language_tag\":\"en_IN\",\"marketplace_id\":\"A21TJRUUN4KGV\"}],\"customRoomType\":[{\"value\":\"Living Room\",\"language_tag\":\"en_IN\",\"marketplace_id\":\"A21TJRU